hasMenuItem.name: 31. Kimchi Bokkeumbap 김치 볶음밥

hasMenuItem.name: 37. Tteokbokki 떡볶이
hasMenuItem.description: A beloved Korean rice cake dish,with a rich history. This enormously popular street food combines chewy rich cakes in a gochujang sauce, creating a spicy, sweet and chewy dish. Addictive!

hasMenuItem.name: 16. Bibimbap 비빔밥

hasMenuItem.description: A variation of our delicious Tteokbokki 떡볶이, this dish combines rice cake rolls with ramen noodles in a gochujang sauce, topped with an egg, creating a spicy, sweet and chewy dish.

hasMenuItem.name: 2. Galbitang 갈비탕
hasMenuItem.description: Luxury among Korean soups for it's cut of meat, this clear broth is soup is made from beef short ribs, cooked until fork tender and stewed with eggs. Hearty yet delicate in flavor. Served with rice or noodles.

hasMenuItem.name: 4. Soondubu 순두부
hasMenuItem.description: Another popular fiery hot soup. This delicious stew is made with silky soft tofu, thinly sliced beef, clams stewed in an beef broth creating deep, spicy flavors. Served with rice.

hasMenuItem.name: 5. Mixed Vegetable with Stone Hot Pot
hasMenuItem.description: A vibrant mix of sautéed vegetables, seasoned ground meat, and a sunny-side-up egg, served in a traditional stone pot.

hasMenuItem.name: 6. Al Bap 알밥
hasMenuItem.description: Literally translating to "Fish roe on rice",  this simple but hearty meal combines flying fish roe "tobiko" with pickled radishes and imitation crab on a bed of white rice. A meal with texture, favor and nourishment.

hasMenuItem.name: 8. Bulgogi 불고기
hasMenuItem.description: One of the most well-known Korean traditional food, this popular bbq dish combines thinly sliced marinated beef, grilled with vegetables. Served with white rice. Korean Bbq for one.

hasMenuItem.name: 9. Bibim-naengmyeon 비빔냉면 (Family size)
hasMenuItem.description: This cold soup-less noodle dish is a perfect way to beat the summer heat. Chewy buckwheat noodles marinated in a spicy, sweet and tangy sauce. A summer treat that can be enjoyed all year.  Please note, this is family sized.

hasMenuItem.name: 10. Bukeoguk 황태해장국
hasMenuItem.description: Hungover or need a break from the hearty and heavy? This delicious delicate clear broth soup is just what the doctor ordered. Made from dried pollack, which is known to have detoxifying effects, eggs, radish and bean spout. Served with white rice.

hasMenuItem.name: 11. Mul Naengmyeon 물냉면
hasMenuItem.description: This cold and refreshing noodle soup is another way to cool down and beat the heat. Made from chewy buckwheat noodles accented with cucumber, shredded beef, thinly sliced radishes and half an egg, The cold savory broth is the main show here. Insider tip: best paired with any of our bbq meat dishes.

But the main player is the sweet potato starch noodles (glass noodles). However you don't have to wait for special occasions to enjoy this delicious dish.
